OL,3,CRegrets, 20mph and tax: The key
OL,4,Cmoments as parties took aim at each
OL,5,Cother
OL,7,FThree party representatives took to
OL,8,Fthe stage for ITV Cymru Wales' debate
OL,9,Fon Sunday night, covering topics
OL,10,Fincluding tax, immigration, and the
OL,11,Fcost of living.
OL,13,FThey were also each given the
OL,14,Fopportunity to cross-examine one
OL,15,Fanother.
OL,17,FBehind the podiums were Conservative
OL,18,FWelsh Secretary David TC Davies,
OL,19,FLabour shadow Welsh Secretary Jo
OL,20,FStevens and Plaid Cymru's Westminster
OL,21,Fleader Liz Saville Roberts.
