OL,7,FSo what were the key takeaways from
OL,8,FSunday's head-to-heads?
OL,10,F"Any regrets?"
OL,12,FAll the representatives were given the
OL,13,Fopportunity to cross-examine their
OL,14,Fpolitical rivals. Plaid Cymru's Liz
OL,15,FSaville Roberts asked the Conservative
OL,16,Frepresentative if he had any regrets.
