OL,3,CRegrets, 20mph and tax: The key
OL,4,Cmoments as parties took aim at each
OL,5,Cother
OL,7,FShe said: "After 14 years of
OL,8,FConservative rule, public services in
OL,9,Ftatters, mortgages through the roof
OL,10,Fbusinesses struggling, what is your
OL,11,Fbiggest regret?"
OL,13,FDavid TC Davies replied: "I haven't
OL,14,Fgot any regrets, public services in
OL,15,FWales as you know are for the Welsh
OL,16,FLabour Government which you've been
OL,17,Fpropping up so I think you should take
OL,18,Fsome responsibility for the fact that
OL,19,Fwe've got the lowest educational
OL,20,Fstandards in the whole of the UK and
OL,21,Fthe longest waiting lists."
