OL,3,CRegrets, 20mph and tax: The key
OL,4,Cmoments as parties took aim at each
OL,5,Cother
OL,7,FJo Stevens said: "What we do now,
OL,8,Fbecause statistics have just come out,
OL,9,Fis that in the first three months of
OL,10,Fthe 20mph policy road accident
OL,11,Fcasualties are down by a third. That's
OL,12,Fhundreds of people in Wales who have
OL,13,Fnot been injured or have not been
OL,14,Fkilled as a result of that policy."
OL,16,FJo Stevens was asked if she had
OL,17,Fconfidence in the Welsh Government's
OL,18,FFirst Minister. She replied,
OL,19,F"Absolutely".
OL,21,F"Paying more tax?"
