OL,7,FIn her question to Liz Saville
OL,8,FRoberts, Ms Stevens asked about Plaid
OL,9,FCymru's tax commitments. She said:
OL,10,F"Would people pay more tax for Plaid
OL,11,FCymru's policies?"
OL,13,FMs Saville Roberts replied: "The
OL,14,Fproposals that we are making would
OL,15,Fmean the broadest shoulders carry the
OL,16,Fweight.
OL,18,F"If we then we have to find a way of
OL,19,Ffunding them."
