OL,3,CRegrets, 20mph and tax: The key
OL,4,Cmoments as parties took aim at each
OL,5,Cother
OL,7,FThe Welsh Secretary said: "I have a
OL,8,Fconcern that your policy of self ID
OL,9,Fwould mean that people who are
OL,10,Fphysically male will be able to take
OL,11,Fpart in sports with women and would
OL,12,Fhave access to single sex spaces where
OL,13,Fwomen would expect to have privacy -
OL,14,Fwhether that would be changing rooms,
OL,15,Ftoilets, hospital wards or even
OL,16,Fprisons."
OL,18,FLiz Saville Roberts dismissed the
OL,19,FConservative's comments as "a
OL,20,Fdistraction". She said, "you have long
OL,21,Fplayed this line of hatred".
